Enter to the TTY mode, press ctrl + alt + f1 

Method1
1. sudo apt-get remove --purge -y lightdm
2. sudo apt-get autoremove --purge -y
3. sudo apt-get install lightdm -y
4. sudo systemctl start lightdm.service
5. sudo reboot

Method2
1. sudo ubuntu-drivers list
2. sudo ubuntu-drivers autoinstall
3. sudo systemctl restart lightdm.servie
4. sudo reboot
